casebody.data:
Third Department,

May, 1941.

(May 7, 1941.) Mabel L. Crane, as Administratrix, etc., of Arthur Morton Crane, Jr., Appellant, v. The State of New York, Respondent. (Claim No. 24038.)

Motion to prosecute appeal as a poor person on typewritten record and brief granted. Present — Hill, P. J., Bliss, Heffeman, Schenck and Foster, JJ.
